What you are missing is that *You do not need another `do..while` loop*

All you need to do is:
 - Read file line by line
 - Save an `Item` if a line with &quot;DONE&quot; is found (Use `contains` instead of `startsWith()`, it&#39;s more intuitive and force user not to mix up &quot;DONE&quot; with other lines)
